        "text": "et al.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). This is most in keeping with the mode of conceiving the matter natural to the evangelist. The visible fact was a fresh fit, and the explanation, from the possession point of view, that the spirit, seeing Jesus, and knowing that his power was at an end, made a final assault.",
